Auth Flow:

1 - Splash Screen (App Branding - Auto login check - initinial data loading)

2 - Welcome Screen (Welcome To our App [Proceed])

3 - Login / Register Screen

4- Login Screen (phone number + password + Forgot Password? )

5 - Register Screen (User data + Terms Accept)

Main App Flow :

6 - Home Page (Search FilterBar + All apartments + Notifications Button)

7 - Filter Search Screen (
selectedGovernorates (Check Boxes)
minPrice - maxPrice (domain)
startDate Calender
endDate Calender
roomCount check 1 2 3 4 or 5+
)

7 - Apartment Details Screen (
title,
descreption,
governorate,
address,
pricePerMonth,
rating,
images,
roomCount
)

8 - Booking Screen (
Date selection ,
total price ,
Payment Method [Sham Cash - MTN - VISA - Paypal - Cash],
Confirm Button (Send Request and Navigate to My Booking Screen)
)

USER PROFILE & MANAGEMENT

9 - My Bookings Screen (
A list Of Booking Card Have :
title and address and total price and date issued And Status:
Pending -> light Black , Confirmed -> blue , Completed -> Green , cancelled - > Grey , Rejected -> Red
)

10 - Booking Details Screen (
Booking Status
Check Out (for fake completing)
Modify-Cancel options
Rate & Review (After check out)
)

11 - My Favorites Screen

12 - Settings Screen ( have :
1 - Profile Card to profile page
2 - Favorites
3 - Dark/Light Theme toogle
4 - Notifications
5 - Currency
6 - Join Us As Investor (Optional)
7 - Log Out

)

12 - Profile Details Screen (Details And Edit Button And Delete Button[5 sec Counter before confirm deleting])

13 - Edit Profile Screen :
(
Update personal info,
change Password,
)

